# Numerical data / model artifacts
# -----------------------------
*.npy
*.npz
*.pt
*.pth
*.ckpt
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.joblib
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.onnx
*.bin

# -----------------------------
# Logs / temp
# -----------------------------
*.log
*.tmp

